Italian Government Denies Plan for Tax Evasion Amnesty

-- B y   A n d r e w   D a v i s
-- 
2011-10-07T16:29:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/italian-government-denies-plan-for-tax-evasion-amnesty.html
Prime Minister Silvio Berlsuconi’s
government denied that it was considering a plan for an amnesty
on tax evasion or other transgressions as part of efforts to
improve public finances.  “The government hasn’t taken into consideration the
hypotheses of amnesties,” Berlusconi’s office said in an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Davis at 
 abdavis@bloomberg.net  